https://www.apollographql.com/docs/apollo-server 

******************************
$env:NODE_ENV="development" or "production" for windows 10 in powershell
setting in package.json --->  "build": "webpack --config webpack.%NODE_ENV%.js"

******************************
launch typescript server:
1)npm run build
2)npm run start
 
include ignore next folders and files:
dist
node_modules
package-lock.json

******************************

WARNING:
if you not use .env, you need delete parametrs "--require dotenv/config"
in package.json, block "scripts"